article.description: — Anwar Gill had 21 points in La Salle's 81-62 victory against Coppin State on Sunday.
article.headline: Gill scores 21, La Salle defeats Coppin State 81-62
article.linkText: Gill scores 21, La Salle defeats Coppin State 81-62
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Anwar Gill had 21 points in La Salle's 81-62 victory against Coppin State on Sunday. Gill added nine rebounds for the Explorers (5-1). Khalil Brantley scored 15 points and added five rebounds and six assists. Jhamir Brickus was 4 of 10 shooting, including 3 for 7 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 5 from the line to finish with 14 points, while adding six assists and four steals. Greg Spurlock finished with 15 points for the Eagles (0-7). Camaren Sparrrow added 14 points for Coppin State. Zahree Harrison also had 14 points. The loss is the seventh in a row for the Eagles. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
